contracts.name: TaikoL1Contract
descriptions: This contract provides functionalities for proposing, proving, and verifying blocks.

contracts.name: GuardianMinorityProver
descriptions: Verifier contract for blocks proven by Guardian minority.

contracts.name: ProverSetProxy
descriptions: A contract that holds TKO token and acts as a Taiko prover. This contract will simply relay `proveBlock` calls to TaikoL1 so msg.sender doesn't need to hold any TKO.

contracts.name: SgxVerifier
descriptions: Verifier contract for SGX proven blocks.

contracts.name: GuardianProver
descriptions: Verifier contract for Guardian proven blocks.
